Back in black and white for Marie Chouinard, who presents her two new group choreographies at Danse Danse: the first inspired by the ink and poems of Henri Michaux, the second inspired by the famous piano solos of Gymnop√©dies de Satie.
An evening that allows you to see the whole Chouinard prism, from art to tics and from black to ink to white.
